OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778602268
OL,3,CThree sentenced for contempt of court
OL,4,Cduring manslaughter trial
OL,6,FThree people have been sentenced for
OL,7,Fdiscussing evidence during an ongoing
OL,8,Fmanslaughter trial.
OL,10,FDuring a six-week trial that started
OL,11,Fin December 2024, Ryan Wellings, from
OL,12,FBispham in Lancashire, was accused of
OL,13,Fthe manslaughter of Fleetwood mum
OL,14,FKiena Dawes.
OL,16,FKiena, 23, was subject to a "campaign
OL,17,Fof abuse" that led to her taking her
OL,18,Fown life by partner Ryan Wellings,
OL,19,FPreston Crown Court heard during his
OL,20,Ftrial.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
