FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778602268
OL,3,CThree sentenced for contempt of court
OL,4,Cduring manslaughter trial
OL,6,FWellings, of no fixed address, was
OL,7,Feventually acquitted of manslaughter,
OL,8,Fbut found guilty of engaging in
OL,9,Fcoercive and controlling behaviour and
OL,10,Fassault occasioning actual bodily harm.
OL,12,FHe had been warned by Judge Robert
OL,13,FAltham not to discuss his evidence
OL,14,Fwith anybody, but in between giving
OL,15,Fevidence he made a number of phone
OL,16,Fcalls to his girlfriend Emma Croft and
OL,17,Fmother Lisa Green.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
