FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778602268
OL,3,CThree sentenced for contempt of court
OL,4,Cduring manslaughter trial
OL,6,FWellings, being held at HMP Preston,
OL,7,Fwas in the middle of giving evidence
OL,8,Fand, while entitled to speak to family
OL,9,Fand friends, he was not legally
OL,10,Fallowed to discuss his case with them.
OL,12,FThe offences happened between 17
OL,13,FDecember 2024 and 2 January 2025.
OL,15,FWellings was later cleared of
OL,16,Fmanslaughter but found guilty of
OL,17,Fengaging in coercive and controlling
OL,18,Fbehaviour and assault occasioning
OL,19,Factual bodily harm and was jailed for
OL,20,Fsix and a half years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778602268
OL,3,CThree sentenced for contempt of court
OL,4,Cduring manslaughter trial
OL,6,FWellings, Croft, and Green admitted to
OL,7,Fcommitting contempt of court by
OL,8,Fdiscussing evidence during the trial
OL,9,Fperiod when they appeared at Preston
OL,10,FCrown Court in April 2026.
OL,12,FLast year, Green and 51-year-old
OL,13,FMichael Wellings appeared at the same
OL,14,Fcourt where they admitted to
OL,15,Fkidnapping their granddaughter ` who
OL,16,Fcannot be named for legal reasons -
OL,17,Fweeks after Kiena's death in 2022.
OL,19,FGreen, Croft, and Michael & Ryan
OL,20,FWellings were sentenced on Friday 8
OL,21,FMay for their offences.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
