PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778602268
OL,3,CThree sentenced for contempt of court
OL,4,Cduring manslaughter trial
OL,6,FRyan Wellings was jailed for a further
OL,7,Fseven months.
OL,9,FGreen, of Haddon Road, Bispham, was
OL,10,Fgiven a 15-month custodial sentence,
OL,11,Fsuspended for 20 months. The 53-year-
OL,12,Fold was also given a 26-week curfew
OL,13,Fbetween 7pm and 6am and 20
OL,14,Frehabilitation activity requirement
OL,15,Fdays.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
