CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778602268
OL,3,CThree sentenced for contempt of court
OL,4,Cduring manslaughter trial
OL,6,FMichael Wellings, of Housman Close,
OL,7,FBispham, was given a nine-month
OL,8,Fcustodial sentence, suspended for 20
OL,9,Fmonths. He was also given a 26-week
OL,10,Fcurfew between 7pm and 6am and 20
OL,11,Frehabilitation activity requirement
OL,12,Fdays.
OL,14,FCroft, 29, of Sandpiper Avenue in
OL,15,FPoulton-le-Fylde, was given a six-
OL,16,Fmonth custodial sentence, suspended
OL,17,Ffor 20 months.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
